profile:
Interior Painting
We understand that we are guests in your house. The utmost respect is paid to maintaining an environment that is as safe and clean as possible.

Preparation
We use clean plastic drop sheets on all furniture.
Durable canvas drop sheets cover the floor.
During sanding, plastic sheets will be taped over entrances to contain the dust.
If requested by customer, all holes and cracks are filled and feather sanded to ensure all edges are smoothed.
Finish Coat

Top grade paints are applied to ensure quality and a job that is washable and durable.
All cut lines and edging are neat and clean.

Commercial
We know that your company’s appearance leaves a lasting impression with your clients, and with the help of experienced painters, you can make it a great one. We understand that work must go on in the work place so we endeavour to work around your business schedule. We do this by painting one room at a time or scheduling weekend work to make sure your business is not disturbed.

No VOC (volatile organic compound) paints are used, keeping office air fresh and healthy for all employees. From start to finish, your commercial painting project will receive attention to detail that only experience can offer.
Back to Top


Exterior Painting
Proper preparation of any painting project is the ground work to ensuring a long-lasting, quality job. With this in mind, our painters will:

Thoroughly power wash entire exterior surface if requested, or the project requires it
Cover all landscaping, bushes, driveways and other non-painted areas as required
Seal all cracks in wood, brick or stucco to seal out moisture
Hard scrape to remove all loose and peeling paint
Light sand all scraped areas to take some of the edges off
Provide optional feather sanding, using power sanders and additional hand sanding which leaves no edges where the previous layers existed
High grade primers are applied to the thoroughly prepped areas to seal in bare spots. The Finish Coat is what seals the thoroughly prepped surface and is what gives the fresh look that you and your neighbours will admire. Top of the line Sherwin William, Homestead House and Benjamin Moore paints are typically used to ensure a quality, long lasting job. Even paint coverage is done to provide visual consistency.

Exterior painting serves two important functions:

Protect your investment. Nature’s elements, like UV rays, moisture and Canada’s gruelling winters take their toll on exposed brick and wood over time. It is much more cost effective to prepare the surface and re-paint than to have to replace the material. The second is to provide an aesthetically pleasing finish to your home.

Pride of ownership is evident in many neighbourhoods. The best way to achieve that is that have your biggest investment looking fresh and updated.
Back to Top


Pressure Washing
In addition to painting, we offer pressure washing, which is used for freshening the siding and decking of your property. Many types of mildew, mould and other foreign substances can grow on and around buildings. Pressure cleaning will revitalize siding and wood surfaces making them look new again. These are also used for preparing them for their new finish.

Pressure washing technology combines your household water with environmentally friendly cleansers designed not only to clean, but to deter future mildew growth. Our cleansers are biodegradable and safe around gardens and trees.

This cleaning will be followed by a high pressure rinse to remove the detergents and any remaining dirt, mold, mildew, and peeling paint.

The Perfect Painter is resuming operations and scheduling free estimates for all your Residential and Painting Needs

We are pleased to announce that all Residential renovations are deemed essential, both new and ongoing renovations including painting can continue as per the Provincial Government.

We have also expanded our service areas to include Burlington, Oakville, Milton, Mississauga, Brampton, Toronto, Vaughan, Markham, Newmarket, Aurora, Stouffville, Pickering and Oshawa.

We are GTA'S Top Professional Painting company, with highly skilled trades and a great reputation for customer service. We specialize in Interior & Exterior Painting, Custom Cabinet Refinishing, Staining  and  Staircase Refinishing . We are experts in residential homes and commercial offices. We do complete Home Renovations and we are a licenced General Contractor all in one. We have 3 divisions,  Perfect Painter, Perfect Handyman & Affinity Home Renovations, we are your "One Stop Shop" for all your renovation needs.. We are the only company in Toronto and GTA market that provides Full Services on almost all aspects of Home Renovations within one Team. We have award winning customer service and pride ourselves on making everything right. Having one team that is responsible for all your home or commercial renovation has great value both from quality, accountability and scheduling. From design and build and to as little as our 4 hour handyman repair service, we can accommodate all your needs.

We are the fastest growing Painting and Home Renovation Company in Toronto and the GTA. Our Handymen and Home Renovation Divisions are all Full Service. We have 24 exceptional Professional Painters hand-picked  and 22  finished carpenters/handyman/skilled trades, they are also Hand-picked. We only hire the best people possible and stand behind all work we do. From small Painting jobs to Handyman Jobs to painting your home and office, we can accommodate all your needs.  Our renovation teams  can complete full condo to home renovations even from the Design and build stages with our skilled staff. Our  highly skilled Field Managers bring an average of 20 years of Construction experience and renovation experience to our company.  We have a real warranty, we will come back and fix something without the fear of people not answering your call or making excuses, we stand behind the work we do.
 
Perfect Painters can provide you with certified color consultants and interior designers. We recommend the best quality paints from Sherwin William, Benjamin Moore or Dulux. We also understand that painting prices need to be competitive and we will always compete to earn your business and trust.  
 
 
We offer our customers the opportunity to purchase paint at our wholesale prices. Perfect Painter is a  custom painting company,  but we don’t charge a custom price. We want to grow our business long term so that we will become the house painters for you and your family. Do not forget to look at our Painting Specials and remember we provide our painting services in the following communities: Aurora, , Brampton, Burlington, Bolton, Caledon, King City, Mississauga, Milton, Maple, Georgetown, Oakville, Richmond Hill, Markham, Vaughan, Etobicoke, Toronto and all of the GTA. We are your Painting company in the GTA.
 


Perfect Painter’s take pride in performing our work to exceed your standard. We will leave your commercial or residential space clean and tidy so it is usable for your clients and family after we have completed our assignment. Please allow us to visit your site/home/office and provide you with an accurate free estimate. We can advise you on the painting work that will be required at that time and make suggestions on color, decor and finishes. Our painting quotes contain a detailed breakdown of costs and the specific work to be done, the painting materials, and an estimate of the amount of time the painting will take. We are also able to offer other services such as drywall and taping at a fraction of the cost of other companies. Prompt, reliable and efficient services – we assure our clients the best quality painting job for your home or your business. 
 
 
 
At Perfect Painter, we have full liability insurance and our staff is covered by WSIB. Most companies fail to meet this criteria almost 83% of the time.
 
Remember you home is typically your largest asset so don’t take chances on losing it by fly by night companies. We understand our business is competitive and we will earn your business each and every time.

profile:
Executive Touch Painters Toronto is a full service painting and renovating company providing service to residents of Toronto and the rest of GTA.  We specialize in exterior and interior painting of both residential and commercial projects. No job is too big or small for us. We provide a complete range of painting services, and with well over a decade of experience in the industry, ET Painters Toronto has been focusing at providing exceptional service to its clients while maintaining the highest level of integrity. 


At Executive Touch, we don't stop there. We provide full service home renovation services including drywall repair and installation, caulking, stucco work, as well as general contracting work. Our stellar reputation of high quality service and fast and efficient work has helped us to grow our business phenomenally.


Please feel free to phone one of our service representatives who can provide advice and guide you in your renovation project. Our foremen answer our phones and with years of experience behind their back, it ensures you get the right advice and consultation right over the phone. 


We service Toronto, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, Newmarket, Mississauga, Brampton, Milton, Aurora, Etobicoke, Scarborough and the rest of the GTA. Phone us today to transform your property into a marvel!


Why would you choose to use Executive Touch Painters Toronto for your next project:
• We provide Guarantee on all our work 
• Provide full workers compensation 
• 5 million liability insurance 
• Fully bonded workers 
• 30 years of experience in the painting industry
• Hundreds of satisfied clients to provide reference of work 
• Use of top quality paint including Benjamin Moore, Dulux, Behr, Sherwin Williams, Para etc. 
• We are exceptionally clean and tidy and utilize drop sheers for every job.


Home Renovations - remodeling living rooms, living space, corridors, ceilings, flooring. 


Bathrooms - remodeling or building from scratch - experience in tiling, grouting, painting, priming, tile installation (marble, ceramic, laminate), plumbing, bathtub and toilet installation 


Kitchens - remodeling or installation of new kitchen - we do everything from tiling, standard and custom made cupboard installation, backsplash, painting, countertop (laminate or granite) installation, plumbing, etc. 


Painting - priming, painting, puttying, sanding - walls, ceilings (interior only)

profile:

Baeumler Approved Contractor


Demiri Painting & Decorating Services is a Top Rated  Painting company and Home renovation company with years of experience based in Toronto, ON. We serve Toronto as well as surrounding cities including Mississauga, Brampton, Vaughan, Markham, Scarborough and more.

We have over 19 years experience providing quality professional residential and commercial painting services at reasonable prices. We are proud for our reputation for great quality and personal service. Our professional team always works together to ensure a smooth running of job and a high standard of workmanship. Customer satisfaction has been and remains our utmost priority, which is why we we offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee. Our knowledgeable and highly skilled professional painters are trained with minimum 10 years painting experience.

Quality work that is completed on time and within budget, and exceed costumer's expectation, is just the beginning of what we do for our costumer's. Colour is critical when setting the tone and the mood of the home. It is important to select the right colours to ensure continuity and a flow from one area to the next. Demiri experts will work with you to create a paint colour that compliments your home and reflects your personal style.  

Also at Demiri Painting, we can help you with  Home renovations, Condominium renovations, Bathroom renovations, Drywall repair and installation, Stucco repair and removal, Ceilings flattening, Carpentry, Floor installation and much more!

Give us a chance to paint your house, and we guarantee you won't be disappointed.

Why use Demiri painting & decorating to paint your house/office? 

•Two Years Guarantee On All Work Done 
•Full Workers Compensation 
•16+ Years Experience in the Painting Industry 
•Hundreds of Satisfied Clients 
•Top Quality Paints Used including Benjamin Moore, Dulux, Behr, Sherwin Williams, F&B, Ralph Lauren etc 
•Drop sheets to Protect Your Floors and Belongings 
•100% Satisfaction Guaranteed!! 

Interior Painting Services Include: 
•Painting (ie. walls, trim, doors, floors, ceilings, etc.) 
•Staining (ie. banisters, hardwood floors, cabinets, etc.) 
•Faux finishing 
•Stucco Painting and Repair 
•Wallpapering and Removal 
•Drywall Repair and Replacement 
•Plaster 

Exterior Painting Services Include: 
•Painting Exterior Surfaces (ie. windows, brick, doors, eaves, soffits, aluminum siding, etc.) 
•Deck/Fence Staining and Refinishing 
•Power Washing 
•Caulking 

Home Renovations Services includes:
• New build additions
• Kitchen renovations
• Bathroom renovations
• Floor installation
• And much more ...


Your satisfaction is our only goal and we stand behind our work. If you are not 100% satisfied with the quality of our painting, we will work to make it right. We won't leave the job, and you won't be asked to pay until you are pleased with the results. 

Our reputation depends on it.

profile:
Kris's Painting offers full service paint, stucco removal (popcorn ceiling removal), plaster & wallpaper services to meet any need. 
We offer a high quality painting services that are guaranteed to be professional, friendly, clean and done on time!!
 
We offer both residential and commercial services including 

****

* Painting, wall preparation, priming and colour changes
* Plastering, fixing all cracks are nail holes before paint is applied
* Drywall Repairs, from flood and water damage to new pot light installation damage
* Stucco Removal (popcorn ceiling removal) to modernize your space and add value to your home
* Wallpaper Removal and reapplication of new paper or preparation for paint
* Mold Removal on drywall or plaster walls. We always use an Air Scrubber to ensure no airborne particles are released in your home environment. Safety is our number one concern. 
* Basement Flood Repair normally requires a minimum removal of the bottom two feet of drywall, insulation and baseboard replacement and reinstall. 
* Power Washing is recommended before applying new paint or stain to exterior decks, siding and brick. 
 
Each projects is different and will receive a specific quote based on your needs. 
At Kris's Painting we always strive for 100% satisfaction for your project.

We are painting professionals with the purpose of disrupting the market and weeding out a lot of the amateurs.

We strive to have the absolute best customer service experience and always exceed your expectations.

profile:
Thanks for visiting Pretty Painting. My name is Roger LeBlanc and I have been painting for 20 years. I take pride in my work and my ability to get the job done without compromising on it's quality. I have been growing due to word of mouth, and that has truly been an honour for me. I started this business because I love to paint, but more importantly, I wanted to charge people a fair price. I think that price inflation is infiltrating everything around us, and even though I am just one person, I want to be that one person that did what was right by those around me. My prices will never be more than they need to be. That will be my motivation for as long as I get to run my own business.
20 years of doing an honorable service is not enough, I hope to do it for 40 more.                                                                    -Roger LeBlanc

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


Pretty Painting is a company built on the integrity of one man, Roger Leblanc. He was determined to one day open up a business that would shake up the industry. He started working for his uncle when he was 15 years old, and he learned from his uncle that you could do the job right without over charging. 
As he moved on in his career, he worked for multiple large companies that had very different and even opposite views and morals to that of his uncle. These companies charged 2-3 times more than what was necessary or fair for the job. That is when Roger knew he would one day open up his own business and continue what he believed was right. He wanted to create a business built on honor and integrity, and make a proper living for his family, without feeling like he stole from his clients to do so.
Finally! Pretty Painting was born and the feedback has been overwhelming. It has been a humbling experience to see how emotional customers get when they see they didn't have to pay thousands of dollars more than what was necessary to get such a spectacular job done. A job done right IS NOT based on how much monetary incentive there is. It is based on the principles of the people who provide it. 
If you are wondering where you may find a job that will meet all of your expectations and not cost you more than what is reasonable, please contact us and give us the opportunity to give you a quote. You can take the time to compare it to other places and see that the same job can have very different prices!
It's Roger's goal that you see this for yourself and not be taken advantage of. 
The growth of Pretty Painting does not equate to a company becoming wealthy, but a company helping people keep more of the money they work so hard to earn! 

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


Since our official company launch this year, we have had enormous support from our community. Our company goal is being well accepted which is to do the best possible quality job without charging those prices that come along with it. Our prices are fair, honorable and with a balance of not taking more from the customer than what is truly ethical and necessary. 
So we decided to take it a step further! if we are not the best price for the best job, then show us a quote from that cheaper registered company and we will not only match it, but we will take an additional 10% off!

profile:
Owning a home is one of the most important financial and sentimental assets that one can have. Beyond building a financially reliable base, you want a home to match your lifestyle and your dreams. When you work with TK Contracting, you’re going to be getting a service that exceeds all expectations through our licensed and bonded tradespeople. 

Our Company
We at TK Contracting Inc.  Are passionate about the work we do. Our commitment is to work with our clients in order to achieve the best results in the project with a safe and timely manner.  We are dedicated to provide our clients with a high level of satisfaction. 

Heath and Safety Protocols
Our policy at TK Contracting is to maintain a safe working environment for everyone. Compliance with health and safety regulations are all outlined in the health and safety policy of TK Contracting.  Our employees are all trained yearly to follow these safety protocols. In order to reduce the risk of injuries at the workplace. 

COVID19 Precautions 
To keep our clients and workers safe, all workers will have a temperature check, and a log to record. All workers shall sanitize before Jobsite, and wear a mask during the entire day. TK Contracting makes sure every team member is tested before working. We are one of the few companies who follow these precautions.

Guaranteed Workmanship 
Our company ensures that each project is handled with good quality materials and professional knowledge to achieve the highest level of satisfaction. We provide a quality service on every project. TK Contracting offers a free written guarantee of 12 months from the date of completion.

profile:
APV Reno are experienced and highly skilled general contractors, home renovation specialists, and painters providing both residential and commercial general contracting needs in Toronto, Downtown Toronto, North York, Mississauga, Etobicoke and GTA areas in Ontario.

We are licensed home renovators & general contractors with over 20 years of successful experience in home renovations, residential & commercial general contracting, and painting. We also work with other professional construction trades across Toronto and the GTA.

APV Reno’s core business is in Design & Renovations. We specialize in home additions, basement renovations, basement finishing, kitchen renovations, bathroom renovations, and general higher-end residential construction.

Other home improvement services include both interior and exterior painting (residential, commercial, and industrial), interior and exterior renovations, as well as fulfilling the procurement process to acquire building permits in the City of Toronto and the GTA.

Our honesty, professionalism and meticulous attention to detail has granted us our success in the cutthroat general contractors and home renovations industry. This has subsequently helped our company build long-term relationships with both clients and contractors, enabling us to steadily grow over the last 20+ years. As a valued client, you can have complete confidence in our work.

Lastly, our integrity in achieving success on every contract or job regardless of how small or large the project, is the core component to our success. All in all, we strive to be a highly reputable and one of the best general contractors in Toronto.

Owning a home is one of the most important financial and sentimental assets that one can have. Beyond building a financially reliable base, you want a home to match your lifestyle and your dreams. When you work with TK Contracting, you’re going to be getting a service that exceeds all expectations through our licensed and bonded tradespeople. 

Our Company
We at TK Contracting Inc.  Are passionate about the work we do. Our commitment is to work with our clients in order to achieve the best results in the project with a safe and timely manner.  We are dedicated to provide our clients with a high level of satisfaction. 

Heath and Safety Protocols
Our policy at TK Contracting is to maintain a safe working environment for everyone. Compliance with health and safety regulations are all outlined in the health and safety policy of TK Contracting.  Our employees are all trained yearly to follow these safety protocols. In order to reduce the risk of injuries at the workplace. 

COVID19 Precautions 
To keep our clients and workers safe, all workers will have a temperature check, and a log to record. All workers shall sanitize before Jobsite, and wear a mask during the entire day. TK Contracting makes sure every team member is tested before working. We are one of the few companies who follow these precautions.

Guaranteed Workmanship 
Our company ensures that each project is handled with good quality materials and professional knowledge to achieve the highest level of satisfaction. We provide a quality service on every project. TK Contracting offers a free written guarantee of 12 months from the date of completion.

profile:
OUTLINED HAVEN
Painting

Looking to get a paint job done?
Look no further!
With over 21+ years of experience in the trades, we guarantee the best quality, at affordable pricing.

***FREE ESTIMATES, IN PERSON OR OVER THE PHONE**** (Over the phone estimates will always be an approximate depending on the info provided by the client)

Services we offer, but not limited to are:

-RESIDENTIAL PAINTING
-COMMERCIAL PAINTING
-INDUSTRIAL PAINTING
-EXTERIOR PAINTING
-SPRAY PAINTING
-KITCHEN CABINET PAINTING
-LATEX
-OIL
-CAULKING

We use only the best quality products and tools to guarantee the best finish and most efficient way to perform the tasks given.
To guarantee the best and most durable finish we use only the best paint brands, Including but not limited to:

-DULUX
-BENJAMIN MOORE
-BEHR MARQUEE (BEST FOR EXTERIOR JOBS)

***Again, these are some of the most used paints by our company, however, there are many other excellent brands out there that will also get the job done****

Our main focus and purpose are to build long lasting relationships with our clients. Clients need to feel safe during and after a getting work done, comfortable enough
to call and ask questions, and we are always here to assist.
We are a family oriented and run business based out of Brampton, ON and have been serving the GTA for over 21+ years.
We know our way around your home, office or commercial space. With the outmost professionalism and work ethic we are NOT happy until you are!

Our team is very experienced and will strive to make this journey as stress free as possible, to make sure that you are happy with the work.
PAINT IT ONCE, AND PAINT IT RIGHT!! Is a motto we live by. It's not about speed or the cheapest price, it's about doing the job properly and efficiently without
breaking your pocket. These are hard times and we completely understand.

Our work speaks for itself. However, before the actual paint, there are a few but not limited preparations needed to be done to surfaces and spaces.
Some of these preparations are:

-COVERING ALL FURNITURE
-COVERING FLOOR
-REMOVING COBWEBS FROM WALLS AND CEILING CORNERS
-LIGHT SAND ON SOME WALLS
-REMOVING ON AND OFF ELECTRICAL PLATES
-CAULKING TRIMS AND DOORS WHERE NEEDED
-MINOR DRYWALL REPAIRS AND PATCHING (SANDING AND PRIMING)

With the COVID-19 pandemic, we guarantee the safety of your family and patrons, all our team will wear masks while at the property
and they are all vaccinated.

Any additional information that we might have missed on this ad, do not hesitate to give us a call or send us an email with your inquiry. We are always happy to take our
time explaining anything you might need a better understanding with, and will always take you through the process. We are a family-oriented business and family comes first.
therefore, the safety of your family and yourself is always our priority.

Contact Info:

MIGUEL
CEO/OWNER/PAINT SPECIALIST

-PHONE 647.741.7775
(WE SPEAK ENGLISH AND SPANISH)

-info@outlinedhaven.ca

Best regards
Sincerely,

The Outlined Haven Team

profile:
Paint Your World with Five Star Painting!
At Five Star Painting, we understand the importance of color. From a fresh exterior paint job that improves the curb appeal of your home or business, to interior paint that brings style and feeling to your daily life, paint can make all the difference. Don’t put off that painting project any longer, call the professionals at Five Star Painting and start enjoying your freshly painted home sooner than later.

Contact Five Star Painting for a Free Estimate
If you are ready to get started on your painting project, contact Five Star Painting to schedule your free estimate. Our convenient online calendar allows you to choose the date and time that works with your schedule. Our team will show up at the scheduled time and provide you with an exact price estimate for the job you have in mind. Whether it be an interior project involving painting and wallpaper removal or an exterior project such as pressure cleaning or deck restoration, estimates are always free and provided at no obligation.

Why Should I Choose Five Star Painting?
Good question! We believe we're a step above the competition and that you can have confidence choosing us. This starts with an exact estimate based on actual measurements of your project, then followed up with a thorough walk-through and a 2-year warranty. We pride ourselves in taking extra special care of our customers

profile:
Paint Your World with Five Star Painting!
At Five Star Painting, we understand the importance of color. From a fresh exterior paint job that improves the curb appeal of your home or business, to interior paint that brings style and feeling to your daily life, paint can make all the difference. Don’t put off that painting project any longer, call the professionals at Five Star Painting and start enjoying your freshly painted home sooner than later.

Contact Five Star Painting for a Free Estimate
If you are ready to get started on your painting project, contact Five Star Painting to schedule your free estimate. Our convenient online calendar allows you to choose the date and time that works with your schedule. Our team will show up at the scheduled time and provide you with an exact price estimate for the job you have in mind. Whether it be an interior project involving painting and wallpaper removal or an exterior project such as pressure cleaning or deck restoration, estimates are always free and provided at no obligation.

Why Should I Choose Five Star Painting?
Good question! We believe we're a step above the competition and that you can have confidence choosing us. This starts with an exact estimate based on actual measurements of your project, then followed up with a thorough walk-through and a 2-year warranty. We pride ourselves in taking extra special care of our customers

profile:
At CertaPro Painters® of Toronto, ON, we know that finding the right team for your painting project can be overwhelming. With our professionals by your side, the process will be easy and convenient — leaving you time for what matters most. We Do Painting. You Do Life.™


Residential House Painting

Experience and Care at Every Stage – House Painting Services

Finding the right team to paint your home can feel overwhelming, but with CertaPro Painters® you’ll have peace of mind. We are experts in residential painting that treat your home with the care it deserves. Our home and residential painting experience is delivered with certainty in these simple steps:

Step One: We connect.

Get started on your painting project by doing a free online estimate. Our team can also come to your home and discuss additional details of your project during a time that’s convenient for your schedule.

Step Two: We consult.

Before preparing a detailed proposal, we will do a walk-through of your space. We’ll also get to know you and your home through our Certainty Pledge®, so that we can customize the way we work with your daily routine.

Step Three: We paint.

Working from your project’s detailed proposal, the painting crew will provide best-in-class service, including cleaning up at the end of each workday. A job supervisor will manage the team, deliver daily updates to you and address your feedback along the way.

Step Four: We follow up.

In addition to a final on-site inspection, an independent quality assurance team may contact you after your project is done to get feedback on your project’s final results and your overall experience with CertaPro Painters®.

Commercial Painting (Multi-Family, Industrial, Retail, Healthcare, Hospitality, Schools)

The requirements of a commercial painting project demand a disciplined and focused approach from the very start. Our team of commercial painting specialists is committed to delivering a quality experience and professional results on every project, every time.

We plan diligently.

A CertaPro Painters® estimating specialist will make an on-site visit and create a proposal that addresses the specific requirements of the RFP. Upon acceptance, we develop a project-specific plan to ensure that the process goes smoothly and that all elements of the project are executed as promised.  We have long standing relationships with our paint vendors who can provide specific job specs and warranties for each and every individual project. 

We respect the schedule.

We arrive at the job site on time and complete each day’s work when we promise we will. If off-hours work is required, or if there are any unique timing needs, we’re more than happy to accommodate them.

We respect the surroundings.

Our work is planned and executed around each property’s specific requirements, with minimized disruption to customers, employees, residents or tenants.

We manage the project so our clients don’t have to.

A job site supervisor is on site during the project to ensure that the work progresses as planned. This enables us to address any issues as they arise and keeps the work on track.

We’ll track our progress for you with and address your feedback along the way. Upon completion of your project, a final site inspection will allow you to review our work in detail.

There is education and preparation that needs to occur so your project goes smoothly and according to your expectations. We do this through a process of communication and education so we can co-create the best possible painting experience with you. We call this the Certainty Service System. At CertaPro, you'll never be surprised. You can be assured that we will always deliver superior service that is on time and on budget. We are a company with a culture of respect. profile:
A family tradition since 1920.

Mark Hooper and Roger Phinnemore are cousins. They come from a long line of painters, but they never thought that they would be carrying on the family tradition. 
The Phinnemore’s have been in the painting business since the 1880’s when James Phinnemore and his sons Roy and Herb began painting residences and businesses in Toronto.  
Mark and Roger’s Great Grandfather Herb began his own company, focusing on residential painting, in 1920.  

H.H Phinnemore and sons became a prosperous business and soon Herb’s sons, Vic, Herb and Roger joined in the venture, followed by their sons.  In the 1980’s Mark and Roger started painting as teenagers working for their Grandfather Herb, Uncles Roger and Steve Phinnemore and learning the business.  Through high school, and later university they painted in the summer to pay for school.  Eventually, what began as a great summer job or a skill to fall back on, turned into their livelihood.  Mark and Roger began Phinnemore and Hooper Painting in 2003. 

Since then their business has been steadily growing, serving Whitby, Ajax, Pickering, and Scarborough areas.  They love to see the results of a beautiful paint job. There is nothing like seeing the satisfaction of a customer when they come home to their house exactly how they left it, only it’s a different colour!  They strive, just like those that went before them to give their customers the best paint job possible with the least amount of worry.  

I guess painting is in the blood after all.

As of 2012 we're now known as Hooper's Painting. 

We work by a set of values that are incorporated throughout our business including:

Quality Workmanship
We do not cut corners. 
We prepare surfaces properly prior to painting.  
We repair walls, fill screw pops, holes and imperfections.  
We caulk cracks in trim. For exterior jobs, surfaces are scraped and sanded.  
We use only premium quality paints and primers.

Pride
We take pride in our work and in the satisfaction of a job well done.

Integrity
We do what we say. You can count on us to arrive when we say we will, to complete a job in a timely fashion in consecutive days, and maintain a high quality of work. 
Our quote is firm and will not change unless the scope of work is changed.

Responsibility
When we take on a job it becomes “our” job.  We are responsible for ensuring our customers satisfaction. 
If something goes wrong we take responsibility.  We carry a $5 million dollar liability insurance policy to back up our claim.

Customer Satisfaction
We work with our customers in order to minimize the disruption which is inevitable in painting.  
We work in an orderly fashion arranging with our customers which areas we will be painting and when.

Cleanliness
We cover all furniture and floors with drop cloths. We limit dust by sealing off working areas during sanding.  
We clean up the job site when we are finished for the day and when the job is finished.  
This includes vacuuming, sweeping, and replacing any furniture we have moved.

Success
Success is defined by us as a satisfied customer. 
We want the customer not only to receive a great paint job, but to feel like they had a pleasant service experience overall as well.

Start and finish on time.
Keep the project neat and clean.
Handle all the details.
Deliver a high-quality painting job you can be proud of.

We serve clients across Durham Region in Pickering, Ajax, Whitby, Oshawa, North York, Markham, Toronto, Scarborough and more.

Improve the look – and value – of your home or business. 

Contact us today for your free estimate.
Call Us - (416)-989-0479
Email us: info@wepaint.ca

profile:
Sivas Painting Inc team is proud to be one of the most modern lead painting companies in the city.

We at the Sivas Painting Inc company are pleased to offer you a wide professional variety of painting services. We strive to hire only the best painters to take care of all our residential & commercial house projects.

We value both the technical and aesthetic sides of our job in every Showcase… Our board of members, managers, as well as all the painters all firmly stand behind the quality control process, and have the drive to keep perfection and passion at every step. This is evident if you take a short glimpse of our “Project Image Gallery”, that highlights our craftsmanship and professional edge.

ENVIRONMENT FRIENDLINESS
Where our competitors adhere to the regular standards of work, … we strive to match those and beat all expectations by ensuring the best practices for environmental friendly work ethics. What you see as the final work, also has a lot of care and thought process to make sure the jobs are done with the up most respect and care for the environment.

SEASONED PROFESSIONALS
We ensure that our employees are not just amateur painters! We dive deep into a training program for our employees to dive deep into the technicality of paint – among many which include: Color Matching, Functionality / Design Based Paint Selection, Technical aspects of application, Environmental Policies Adherence, …….much much more..We are therefore, very proud and depend a great deal on the professional rarity of our employees – so we also take a bold stand on providing all our projects with a warranty that you can lean on.

***

The work done BEFORE paint is applied is critical to a beautiful final product. Our painters provide expert invisible patching and repairs to walls, ceilings and trim on all surfaces such as plaster, drywall and wood. We do stucco repairs as well. Other services include: wallpapering, striping and applying special wall finishes such as Venetian plaster. Installing Cornice or other moldings and dry walling small areas are also available. Having worked with a wide array of clients over the years John Bell will personally establish exactly what you need and want. profile:
Priority Plus Painters first began in 1989 as a SCARBOROUGH PAINTING COMPANY and has since provided consistent professional painting services to thousands of customers throughout the GTA. We are not brand loyal, and will use any paint not recommended by our company.

Our continued focus is to provide for the client an exceptional and pleasant experience from the first call to the final goodbye. Our knowledge base has grown from being able to master the simplest of tasks to being capable of problem solving almost all of your painting and decorating needs.

With a dedication to excellence we strive to separate ourselves from our competition by simply being the best. There is no RESIDENTIAL PAINTING job in TORONTO too big or small for us to handle.

We begin each project with a focus on preparation. This is the key to providing a professional paint job. Proper preparation provides us with a foundation to deliver a superior finish. From pole sanding walls to filling nail holes and hairline cracks, it is all very crucial to delivering the best finish. We even go as far as to sand in between coats after priming to ensure a smooth surface.
After each day of work Priority Plus Painters will do a thorough cleanup prior to leaving as to leave your home or office in a manageable state.

Interior Paint:
Times change and so do your colour choices. When it comes time to HOME PAINTING in TORONTO and throughout the GTA, allow Priority Plus Painters to bring your home up to speed with fresh colour choices. A new paint job can revitalize an old and tired looking room. Starting! The best way to transcend the look of your home is to hire a professional painting contractor. At Priority Plus Painters we pay attention to every small detail to ensure we deliver to you the finest workmanship possible. Whether there is a new addition to the family or simply just time for a change, painting is a quick and affordable way to enhance your living space or office workplace.

We work with you in the colour selection process and give you access to over 24 years of expertise. Not only colours change over time but also finishes as well. Where glosses and semi-glosses were once common, they have been replaced with flats and eggshells. Let us help you in your decisions for your home or office.

Exterior Paint:
Exterior painting is not simply to enhance the look of your home or office. By professionally maintaining all of the exterior painted surfaces of the home or building it will maximize protection from the sun and other harmful environmental factors. Surface preparation is key to a successful paint job. Priority Plus Painters provides professional workmanship to ensure all exterior surfaces are clean and dry prior to the first application of primer or paint. 

For exterior painting we provide:
Thorough cleaning, scraping, and sanding as needed prior to any application caulking and putty as needed, no painting in direct sunlight as to ensure proper bonding during dry time, using the highest quality paints and stains

Wallpapering:
Priority Plus Painters has been hanging wall coverings for over 24 years. From a simple powder room to national restaurant chains we have made installations. We are experts at professional removal of all wallpapers on a timely basis. Wallpapers come in many styles and forms. From unpasted to pasted, 24”inches to 54” wide, and from woven perforated vinyls to straight paper. Let our expertise in wall coverings assist you with all your wallpaper needs.
Wallpaper Styles
    Handprints
    Fabrics
    Grasscloth
    Foils
    Vinyls
    Murals
    Scenics




Once the colours have been chosen, the painting begins. Our services include:
  - Highest quality paints and stains
  -Expert plaster repair and resurfacing
  -Stripping and refinishing of trim
  -Extensive preparation of all surfaces

For exterior painting we provide:
  - thorough cleaning, scraping, and sanding as needed prior to any application
  - caulking and putty as needed
    -no painting in direct sunlight as to ensure proper bonding during dry time
    -highest quality paints and stains

Wallpaper Installation:
   Wallpaper Styles
   - Handprints
   -Fabrics
   -Grasscloth
   -Vinyls
   -Murals
   -Scenics
Priority Plus Painters is your solution to all of your painting needs.

profile:
Spray-Net's exterior painters will beautify your home in just a day! 

Using our industrial-strength coatings and spraying technique, we bring factory quality results right to your doorstep. We've created a cost-effective service that will instantly boost your home's curb appeal and save you on the cost of completely replacing your siding, doors and windows! Every project results in a permanent factory finish, free of any brush and roller marks, that won't peel and looks absolutely brand-new. Not repainted.
services: We offer a turn-key exterior painting solution. From surface prep to end of day clean-up, our exterior painters take care of everything so you don't have to. No matter the surface we're revamping, all of our projects are backed by a 15-year warranty against peeling and a 10-year warranty against premature fading and discolouration. Like our customers, we like a renovation without all the hassle!
specialities:
We specialize ONLY in exterior painting: Aluminum/Vinyl Siding - Brick - Stucco -  Hardie Board/Fibre Ciment- Aluminum/Vinyl Windows - Front & Garage Doors - Fascia/Soffits/Eavestroughs/Trim. 

Each of our coatings is uniquely tailored to a specific exterior surface for maximum adhesion and an optimal finish. Coupled with our spray application, our coatings result in a permanent, like-new finish that will completely transform the look of your home!

profile:
Patri Paint is a family operated Toronto based company that has been servicing Ontario since 2010. Things to expect from Patri Paint include professionalism, cleanliness, and clear expectations. As our team grows, we continue to solidify our standards by using our training system which has helped us continue to succeed through the years.
- Once your free consultation is scheduled, a team member will visit your site or provide a remote consultation (up to 45 minutes depending on the size of the project). 
​
- A detailed expectation is set regarding the project.
​
- After the project, we leave the job site spotless ✨.
​
- Expect a follow up call from us 2 weeks after project completion to ensure your satisfaction with our service.

MOVING SERVICES

When it comes to moving, Patri Paint stands out mainly because of 2 things, being professional, and being transparent. We are a family business that has helped families and businesses all over Ontario for the last 6 years and pride ourselves in making moving a painless experience for our customers.

Almost 30% of our customers require painting jobs for homes they are ready to put on the market, the increasing demand for moving services has allowed Patri Paint to assist hundreds of families and businesses in Ontario over the last 6 years. All our drivers and movers are fully licensed, trained, and insured.

Up The Wall creates murals and custom paintings for residential homes and commercial establishments. 
Trained artist Michelle Wenger, a mural painter in Toronto, has been creating murals and custom artwork
in Toronto, Canada and Europe for over sixteen years. 
 
At Up The Wall, we specialize in creating custom artwork, dramatic murals, and beautiful paint finishes.
 
We will enhance the look of any interior space, and work directly with clients or their designers. 
We offer digital layouts, so we'll show you what your projects will look like, before a brush ever touches the wall or canvas! 
 
Talk to us today about creating murals or artwork for your children, your home, or your business.

products:
We recommend and use a number of paints with Benjamin Moore being our first choice. We also use Para, Glidden, Sherwin Williams often and we're familiar with Farrow & Ball, Ralph Lauren and C2. We tend to pick the product that will best serve our customer's needs both in the practical sense of wear and tear and the artistic sense of colour, brightness and the correct amount of gloss for the area being painted.
We also familiar with the various brands of stains and varnishes such as Minwax, Varathane and others.
In our faux finishes we use Moore's latex glaze most often for the ease of application and its consistency with the colour mixed with the glaze. 
In wallcovering applications we study all the manufacturer's recommendations and use the appropriate wall sizes and pastes.
services:
We primarily paint with brush and roller both interiors and exteriors. 
We apply stains and varnishes. 
We can also recommend tradesmen for other work such as electrical.

J & N Painters is your #1 family owned contracting company trained on all of the latest painting designs, tools and techniques serving you in the Greater Toronto Area (GTA).

You can always count on us to provide you with exceptional communication and extraordinary quality service for the painting project.

Our professionals pay careful attention to every detail in your home and perform a thorough quality inspection after the project is completed.

J & N Painters is unique in comparison to other painting companies because of the following:

- We are a family owned business, and you can trust that we will treat your home like our beautiful home.
- We have successfully completed over 1000 projects in residential and commercial painting contracts.
- We are committed to providing professional service and workmanship with the ability to complete all projects on time.
- We are focused on client service satisfaction and providing exceptional quality of work at an affordable cost.
- We are covered for 5 Million Dollar Business Liability Insurance and through Workplace Safety and Insurance Board. 
- We offer professional and client references  when requested  by potential clients and communicate at all times.
- We use high quality paint brands, such as Sherwin Williams or Benjamin Moore, depending on your project budget.
- We will follow up with you and your project, at the beginning, middle and end of the project. Your business is very important to us.
- We are a member of HomeStars
- Free colour consultation is also available from our experts when requested. We sit down to understand your needs and to suggest the colours that is best suitable for you and your home.

profile:
Professional painters believe that spraying is the best way to quickly perform painting of any area with an excellent result. With spray it is possible to create the highest quality painted surface over any size area, without the appearance of leaks, lines, streaks or unpainted areas. This method allows to paint hard-to-reach places, resulting in an even and smooth coat. Spray painting is also great for the decorative and protective painting of the items with different shapes and configurations.
These are the advantages of using spray:
Uniform application of the paint layer;
No traces of roller pile or brush bristles on the painted surface;
High speed of work;
Easy and fast application of paint on large areas.
That’s why we prefer to work with spraying application of paint, and of course we cover and protect all surrounding surfaces from paint. Our painters are highly trained and have years of experience. They are able to work at your convenience – on holidays, weekends and evening shifts to minimize any disruption to your environment. We use supplies and materials of top brand names, such as Benjamin Moore, Sherwin Williams etc.

Unisprayer provides the following services:

new construction
repainting interior and exterior
staining and varnish
wallpaper removal
stucco removal
drywall repair
